long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Search your chrome history via keywords! 

Vulture automatically indexes every website you visit in Chrome, allowing you to find it at a later date.
To use, type 'v' followed by a tab or space key, then enter your desired keywords.

Vulture also has a built in to-do list to help you stay on top of your work!
